description:
A FUNERAL IN BERLIN PART 1

The Torch may not truly be alive, but now he's dying, condemned by the same chemical agent that defeated the Thinker's artificial virus. His only chance? To follow a seventy-year-old trail into the depths of the Bolivian jungle, and face a monstrous parody of himself in a battle to the death!
name: A Funeral In Berlin, Part One

description: The kingdom of Horder is about to be destroyed by the most horrendous and least stoppable force in the world . . . and, amazingly, it isn't Groo! But he's around and making his presence known, which means that he's making things worse. If you didn't buy the first three issues, buy this one, see how it ends, and then go back and find the first three so you have a clue as to what any of it means. From the infamous and award-winning team of Sergio Aragonés and Mark Evanier, with Stan Sakai and Tom Luth and, yes, a real. live letters column!

volume.name: Sergio Aragonés' Groo: The Hogs of Horder

description: With Modeus at last revealed and standing by Plutonian's side, the Paradigm--and the world--have no defense against Armageddon! But is this the end? Or only the beginning? A not to be missed issue of BOOM!’s bestselling apocalyptic superhero ongoing by multiple Eisner Award-winning KINGDOM COME and EMPIRE author Mark Waid.

The beginning of a new Farscape cracker, “Red Sky at Morning.” The crew of Moya take in all they’ve seen recently. Crichton, Aeryn and especially Chiana will never be the same. But soon it will be another member of the ship thrust into the harsh spotlight. They crew visits…Pilot’s homeworld. A don’t miss issue of the new ongoing FARSCAPE series written by the show creator Rockne S. O’Bannon!
name: Red Sky at Morning, Part 1: Refractions of the Way Life Used to Be

description:
Neverland was once a magical paradise until it fell under the rule of the evil being. It has now become a world that haunts children’s nightmares.

Present day Manhattan, a haunted and disturbed Nathan Cross is a grown man with a past he cannot shake and a future that looks hopeless. Wendy Darling is a loyal aunt who takes care of her two nephews whose parents have passed away. But when an evil entity known as Pan enters Wendy’s world, she must seek out the one man who can help her save her family.

Det. John McClane has seen some nasty villains in his time. But this is a first. One of New York City’s most glamorous and beautiful women is causing trouble all across the city thanks to a blackout she engineered. Why would she create such mayhem? The answer will shock NYC’s newest detective! Join legendary industry creator Howard Chaykin in this new ongoing on a thrill ride that's rung up over $1 billion in box office worldwide and become the gold standard for classic action! Yippee Ki Yay!
name: Year One Part Seven

description:
The times are changing, and they've finally caught up to Marvel Boy with bizarre menaces and strange threats to match his power! A mysterious figure with an agenda has also caught up to Bob Grayson. Surrounded by manipulators, how can the Uranian finally become the hero he was born to be? Jeff Parker, writer of the acclaimed series AGENTS OF ATLAS, reveals the untold tale of other-worldly mental marvel! Plus, re-presenting classic Atlas-era tales of the space-boy’s adventures!

Backup Story Titles

  • The Deadly Decision!?
  • The Phantom Pen
  • Unseen Terror!
name: Man Of Two Worlds

description: When one of Uncle Scrooge's rivals, John D. Rockerduck, challenges Donald Duck's favorite uncle to a penny-pinching contest that spans the globe, he says "Bring it on!" Hop in your hot air balloon with BOOM Kids! and follow Scrooge and the gang as they traiblaze on a budget in part 2 of "Around the World in 80 Bucks!"
name: Around the World in 80 Bucks, Part 2

description: “TO RESCUE FROM MONSTERS” The Deathlok protocols have been initiated…and they can be summed in a single word: Demolish. RoXXon Corps is about to learn the cost of its sizzling ratings. In the end, the fate of the world lies in the hands of two men blown to bits long ago on a battlefield, two men with no lost love for each other: hotdog super soldier Lieutenant Mike Travers and the man who killed him, C.O. Luther Manning.
name: To Rescue From Monsters

description:
Fan-favorite artist Michael Avon Oeming (Powers) joins Brandon Jerwa in debuting the latest Red Circle hero – The Fox! Filmmaker Paul Patten Jr. heads from Seattle to the underbelly of Tokyo gangster life, caught up in a mission to discover the truth behind his late father's adventures, but becomes the modern embodiment of the Kitsune totem known as the Fox!

Meanwhile, a new mission kicks off for the Shield – Operation Gunslinger! Hot on the trail of the mysterious H.I.V.E. splinter group Black Seven the Shield must lead a group of special operatives, one of whom strongly has his faith strongly shaken in his commanding officer. Will the Shield uphold his loyalty oath? Or is he about to go AWOL?
name: Operation Gunslinger, Part 1: Down Range; The Fox, Part 1

description: Deep in the swamplands of the planet Mimban lies a powerful crystal, capable of giving its possessor an invincible mastery of the Force. In the right hands, it could save the galaxy. But in the wrong hands, it could destroy it. While the explosion of the first Death Star still reverberates through the cosmos, Luke Skywalker finds that the war he thought he won was only a battle, and that the dark side of the Force still stalks the galaxy.

volume.name: Star Wars: Splinter of the Mind's Eye

description: Imprisoned by the Imperial forces, confronted by two very violent, very massive creatures known as yuzzem, Luke and Leia have only one hope of escape: the Mimban Crystal, capable of giving its wielder total, omnipotent mastery of the Force. But Luke's use of the crystal could draw the unwelcome attention of certain ... dark powers.

volume.name: Star Wars: Splinter of the Mind's Eye

description: Even as Darth Vader and his Imperial garrison approach Mimban from the air, Luke and Leia find that their biggest problems lie under the planet's crust. For deep in the soil lives Mimban's deadliest predator -- perhaps the galaxy's deadliest predator -- the gigantic, wormlike wandrella; and if the humongous wandrella can't catch them, the subterranean race of aboriginals -- the Coway -- just might!

volume.name: Star Wars: Splinter of the Mind's Eye

description: Mimban is like a million other planets in the galaxy -- a lot of trees, too much mud, and not much else. But one of Mimban's abandoned temples holds a powerful gem -- the Kaiburr crystal -- capable of magnifying and clarifying one's perception of the Force. Luke and Leia know it's there -- somewhere -- and so does Darth Vader. And that makes Mimban a whole lot livelier right now than those other planets!

volume.name: Star Wars: Splinter of the Mind's Eye

description: Perpetually caught between Sam and John's arguments, Dean hits a boiling point and drags his brother out for some good ol' monster hunting – at the Museum of Natural History! Time for a little bonding over blood! But the boys' first "hunt" together goes tragically wrong...and has disastrous consequences for Sam.
name: Beginning's End, Chapter Three

description: The Tankies' Sergeant Stiles returns, recently promoted and angrier than ever. He's got a new crew and a new tank, a Sherman Firefly with a high-velocity gun capable of taking out even the fearsome German Tiger. Too bad the enemy have a new tank of their own, the mighty King Tiger, with twice the armour and firepower of the original. As Stiles and his men join the Allied advance into the Nazi homeland, they soon realise that every inch of ground will be bitterly contested by the foe... and that there are worse horrors than Tigers lurking in the gloom of the last German winter.
name: The Firefly And His Majesty Part 1: Welcome To The Fatherland

description:
In a city so dismal it's known only as "the Hole," a clan of Sorcerers have been plucking people off the streets to use as guinea pigs for atrocious "experiments" in the black arts. In a dark alley, Nikaido found Caiman, a man with a reptile head and a bad case of amnesia. To undo the spell, they're hunting and killing the Sorcerers in the Hole, hoping that eventually they'll kill the right one. But when En, the head Sorcerer, gets word of a lizard-man slaughtering his people, he sends a crew of "cleaners" into the Hole, igniting a war between two worlds.

Chapter Titles

  • Spell 1: Caiman
  • Spell 2: Hungry Bug
  • Spell 3: The Nightmare Man
  • Spell 4: In the Bag
  • Spell 5: Eat Quietly During Meals
  • Spell 6: My Neighbor the Sorcerer
  • Extra Evil
name: Vol. 1

description: Since the dawn of time, a being has existed who has shaped human development. His powers have allowed him to secretly remove certain critical days from the historical record, and those events have never been told. But the occurrences of these days have forever changed the course of humanity's evolution. These are the Days Missing from our existence, and they are about to be revealed! Collects all 5 issues of the hit mini-series and includes a cover gallery and sketchbook.
name: Volume 1

description: Jubilee and the X-Men teach kids the dangers of strangers.
name: Safety Net

first_appearance_locations.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

location_credits.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

volume.name: Be X-tra Safe with the X-Men

description:
1. Blue Beetle: The Blue Beetle goes up against the Web. The Web has a ray that can destroy ships, planes and skyscrapers with a single shot. The Beetle also builds his romance with Joan Mason in this eighteen page adventure.
  2. Samson and David: Samson and David take on Nazi spies and stop Johann Sanf from his plans to create havoc on United States soil. This is a thirteen page story.
  3. Bridge in Danger: The Bridge in Danger is a two page short story and is not a comic. Charlie Maxon is an insurance detective who solves the murder of a security guard.
  4. Samson and David: Samson and David bring Baron Siva to Justice in this Thirteen page story.
  5. Flame: In this fourteen paged story, the Flame stops some Nazi saboteurs.
name: Bridge in Danger

description: It's that time of year again! The Marvel Zombies are returning and bringing a SPOTLIGHT-sized passel of ghoulish gore with them! Besides covering the comeback of comic's famous flesh-eaters, we'll be delving into Marvel's rich history of horror, including a special focus on Marv Wolfman and Gene Colan's TOMB OF DRACULA. We'll also be assessing the lay of the zombie landscape with undead appearances in DEADPOOL: MERC WITH A MOUTH and more! Consider this special issue of SPOTLIGHT a menu filled with the most gruesomely gastronomical delights Marvel has to offer. Dinner is served!
name: Marvel Spotlight Marvel Zombies Return

description: October brings our most sepulchral SPOTLIGHT yet, as we unleash legions of Marvel Zombies on loyal Marvel-ites everywhere! We'll be digging up the latest dirt on the hottest undead property in comics, to bring you the best, most behind-the-crypt coverage around: If it's got a pulse, we're not interested! Get ready for an inside look at the past and future of the Marvel Zombies, going back to their creation in Millar/Land's ULTIMATE FANTASTIC FOUR, the breakout-hit limited series by Robert Kirkman and Sean Phillips, the Dynamite crossover series MARVEL ZOMBIES VS. ARMY OF DARKNESS, and all the future comics fun featuring these flesh-eating phenoms! All this and a comprehensive look at the amazing art of Arthur Suydam! PLUS: SPOTLIGHT surveys the landscape of Marvel's universe of magic with the creators who brought you MYSTIC ARCANA! Magic, mysticism and monstrous mayhem: Hand 'em out to the kiddies on Halloween night! It's a Marvel Zombies SPOTLIGHT that's all treat and no trick!
name: Marvel Spotlight Marvel Zombies

description: Once upon a time, in a faraway land called the Mojoverse, a magical being named Longshot set off on a journey in search of Something Important. The only problem was - he didn't know what that Something was. Accompanied by a three-inch tall ceature called Nutt, pursued by a Dark and Fiendish Thingee, Longshot embarked on a adventure that took him from the Door of Death to a Kansas cornfield, from the Gates of Heaven.... to the depths of the human heart.
name: Fools

description: A deep conspiracy is being hatched in Leon, France which is bound to cause a great upheaval in Dhruv's life! Marcella a beautiful female and a crime Lord meet in a park! They specialize in stealing latest inventions from the defense research labs across the globe! Marcella wants to sell off an estate to avoid the suspecting Police! Her father in law has made his will stipulating a clause that his younger son should sign the sale deed. And it turns out that the younger son is none other than Dhruv's father Shyam! Dhruv is the legitimate heir of his father and under the clause should sign the sale deed. Marcella knew that making Dhruv agree to their terms would be a tough nut to crack to hence they decide to have him eliminated! A masked man is overhearing this conversation and is determined to protect Dhruv! He shall try to protect Dhruv and yet avoid making any contact with him. Will the true identity of the masked man be revealed? Dhruv's life is in a total turmoil when a mysterious caller informs him that his father's true identity is Raghuvansi who is wanted by the police for a heinous murder? Join Dhruv is his quest for truth exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Khooni Khandaan(Killer Family)

description: Luka, the son of Marcella has failed twice in his attempt to assassinate Dhruv! Mr. Jacob the owner of Jupiter circus was grievously injured in the attack and is yet to recover his consciousness. Luka hires local goons to assassinate Mr. Jacob! Dhruv manages to foil their attempt and comes to know that Luka and his accomplices have fled to France! Commissioner Rajan pulls up a few strings to help Dhruv travel to France to unravel the mystery! He has asked his friend in police department to extend every possible help in solving the mystery surrounding Dhruv's father! Jigsaw, the famed international smuggler rebukes Luka for undertaking a mission to eliminate Dhruv without having his prior approval! He has high opinion of Dhruv and considers Dhruv as threat for his operation! Jigsaw asks a crime lord to send his henchmen to kill Dhruv mid air. Jigsaw feared that Dhruv could put a spanner on his next robbery plan where the stakes were very high! Dhruv is forced to jump off the plane to save the life of the passengers! Will he survive the fall and solve the mystery surrounding his father? Watch the suave officer Vera in a very exciting role. She proves to be a very useful ally of Dhruv during his quest for justice of his father! Join hands with Dhruv in solving the mysteries of the hidden past exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Atit(Past)

description: Dhruv manages to prove the innocence of his father while the police officer responsible for the macabre murder has been unmasked! Vera has also managed to bury her disturbed past! Vera wishes to thank Dhruv and takes a vacation to accompany Dhruv in his quest! Jigsaw lays a trap to entice Dhruv to a cottage at a desolate place. An alert Dhruv manages to sense danger and escape the explosion. Jigsaw has stolen an invention code named scrambler which can back into any computer system and change its codes and passwords! Jigsaw has induced a mutation in the crime lord transforming him to a monster. The monster attacks Dhruv who is en-route to meet his family! Dhruv shows a lot of resourcefulness to control this monster. Jigsaw has induced a mutation in the crime lord transforming him to a monster. Dhruv finally gets a chance to meet his family, his uncle & aunt and his grand father who is comatose! A masked man's warning arouses Dhruv's suspicion that something is fishy! He decides to stay back and investigate! Jigsaw is holding the world to ransom by controlling passwords to their sophisticated weapons arsenal! It's up to Dhruv to redeem the situation! Dhruv battles it out with jigsaw and his evil relatives to uphold justice! Read the thrilling and concluding episode of the adventure, exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Jigsaw

description: Dhruv's past has come back to haunt him! The owner of globe circus, Boss has come back to his senses after a prolonged coma and is plotting to seek revenge from Dhruv. He has found the perfect weapon to neutralize Dhruv; Nakshatra! Nakshatra skills are at par with Dhruv in every aspect! He is an acrobat par excellence and performs stunts in the circus to support his crippled father! Boss first overtakes the circus in which Nakshatra and his father used to work. Boss hatches a well planned scheme to have Nakshatra's father killed in an encounter by commissioner Rajan! His cunning plan is executed by his loyal associates who first instigate Nakshatra's father to point a revolver at commissioner Rajan. On of the associates forces Commissioner Rajan to fire at Nakshatra's father! Nakshatra is made to believe that Commissioner Rajan is a brutal cop who murdered his father in cold blood. Nakshatra vows to assassinate Commissioner Rajan and seek revenge for his father's death! The plan had its desired effect with Dhruv and Nakshatra are locked in a duel. What remains to be seen is whether Nakshatra will kill Dhruv? Dhruv and Nakshatra share uncanny similarities far as their upbringing and their skills were concerned! Will Dhruv manage to rein Nakshatra and stop him from committing the murder of Commissioner Rajan? Get hooked to the thrilling adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Jung(Battle)

description: Vidushak was a proclaimed offender for serious crimes but could not be prosecuted since he was able to prove that he was mentally unfit to undergo a trail. This dangerous criminal was being transferred to the asylum at Rajnagar. Vidushak manages to give the asylum authorities the slip, only to face Dhruv! But Dhruv had no measure of his opponent and Vidushak was able to throw few surprises at Dhruv and eventually managed to escape! Vidushak comes to know that his gang is being harassed by Haroon Shah Gang. He decides to assassinate Haroon Shah and heads for his yacht. Shweta is dating Shantanu. Shantanu invites Shweta to a yacht which incidentally belongs to Haroon Shah. In a case of mistaken identity Vidushak attacks Shantanu's father, taking him to be Haroon Shah. Vidushak is searching for a painting and blackmails Dhruv to hunt for it! Dhruv is a desperate man with her sister's life at stake! He is ready to accede to the demands of a criminal like Vidushak. So, is there more than that meets the eye? The answer is yes and you can find it out in a thrilling adventure available exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Dushman

description: Mr. K Mahendru the director of the famous TV serial quiz hour, and Mr. Bryan, the host for the show, have been kidnapped by Quiz Master Tito! Quiz master Tito was dumped from this prestigious show because he had developed a knack for asking weird puzzles and riddles to the contestants! Tito kidnapped the duo to extract his vengeance! The ransom note was in the form of a riddle and the deadline for meeting the demands of the Kidnapper was approaching! Unable to solve the riddle the police call in Dhruv to help them out. Now Dhruv is in a race against time and has to solve the riddle on the ransom note to locate whereabouts of Tito. Dhruv manages to solve the puzzle and locate the kidnapper before it's too late! Tito tries to trap Dhruv but Dhruv proved to be made of a sterner stuff! Tito makes an exit once he realizes that Dhruv is a tough net to crack! Tito acknowledges Dhruv as a worthy opponent and promises to leave him a clue in the form of a riddle before a crime is committed! The onus is on Dhruv to crack the riddle and prevent Tito from committing the crime. Dhruv is being tested by Quiz Master Tito who leaves him with a new riddle to solve! Dhruv is on hot pursuit of this elusive villain who manages to give him the slip time and again! So how does our favorite superhero out wit his clever opponent? Solve this puzzle by flipping through the page of the new adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Quiz Master

description: In order to earn some extra pocket money Shweta volunteers as a tourist guide to an American tourist party. Dhruv gifts her transmitter to communicate with Karim in case she needs any information pertaining to her trip to the ancient palace of Zajbal Dauri. The tourist party is attacked by the terrorists who wish to seek mileage from the killings of international terrorists and politicize the issue of Kashmir! Dhruv is warned about the terrorist attack by Karim who was having a radio contact with Shweta! Dhruv reaches the spot to find Chandika fighting the terrorists. Dhruv Chandika and Vikram a young American whiz kid in electronics who was part of the tour helps the duo of Dhruv and Chandika to nab the terrorist! Shweta remerges to continue as their guide and narrates a story pertaining to a hidden treasure of Zaj-bali who was the last emperor of the Dauri clan. According to legend the mummy awaits the return of the true heir to the king's throne who shall seek his rightful claim on the treasure! Vikram is convinced about the authenticity of the story and is determined to hunt for the treasure and the guardian mummy! Has Dhruv been lured to open a Pandora's Box by inviting the displeasure of the ancient mummy? An ancient destructive force is about to be unleashed which will cause wide spread destruction in Rajnagar! The quest for treasure continues exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Mummy Ka Kahar

description: Many small gangs have sprung up in the slums of Rajnagar. Each gang extorts protection money from the people residing in their territory. Commissioner Rajan fears that sooner or later Rajnagar will witness a battle for supremacy between these gangs. But mayor Savaria refuses to grant permission to act against these gangs. A shady character named Guardian murders the leader of the Thunderbolt gang; the second largest gang in Rajnagar and frames up Alligator gang for the murder! He then provides sophisticated weaponry to the Thunderbolt gang to wipe out their enemy, the Alligator gang! Dhruv has been informed about the attack! Can Dhruv prevent the massacre? Is Guardian weaving a sinister trap around Dhruv? Will he succeed in defeating Dhruv is determined to rein the mayhem on the streets of Rajnagar? Why is Mayor Savaria sympathizing with these goons? Dhruv finds two valuable allies in the form of Black Cat & Justice in his crusade against the street gangs! Witness as a war unfolds, exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Commando Force

description: Bauna Vaman has been cooling his heals in the high security prison of Narka jail. The entire prison was guarded by the latest state of the art security system provided by a Japanese firm named Yukaharo Electronics. A criminal named Tronica equipped with the latest gizmos breaks through the security parameter and manages to rescue Bauna Vaman! Tronica wishes to assign Bauna Vaman a contract to steal a security chip from Yukaharo Electronics. Tronica pays him an advance of five crores to accomplish his mission. Incidentally Shweta was working in Yukaharo Electronics as a summer intern! Yukaharo Electronics had developed a chip with amazing features, but its true nature was highly confidential! Vaman manages to steal the chip but the whole job wasn't as smooth as he anticipated! Dhruv, Chandika, a samurai warrior are in hot pursuit of Vaman, where as Tronica is not a man to be trusted. The action paced adventure is heading towards an exciting climax where the protagonists keep fighting against each other! What's so special about this chip? Who is Tronica and how did he manage to bypass the security at Narka Jail? Set the adrenalin racing exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Bauna Waaman

description: Scientists working for Natasha have managed to create a new metal named Vibranium! Vibranium has a unique property of absorbing all forms of sound energy. It could also harness this sound energy and release it in the form of weapon of mass destruction. This was possible by using sound energy converter which could convert matter into sound waves. Natasha informs the leading terrorist organization about using Vibranium as a weapon and invites bids for the new weapon! The same night, Dhwani Raj attempts to usurp the invention. Natasha is cornered and faces an execution squad, when Dhruv intervenes as a knight in shining armor! Dhruv had figured out the fighting style of Dhwani Raj earlier and was able to ward off his attack with ease. Dhwani Raj knew the futility of attacking Dhruv and hence attacked Natasha instead! Natasha wasn't able to fend the attack and crashed with the converter and vanished in thin air! Was Natasha dead? Will Dhruv manage to seek revenge against Dhwani Raj? Ninad a mysterious creature is out to seek Dhwani Raj! Is she a friend or a foe? Satisfy your curiosity in a smashing adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: KaalDhwani

description: A robbery was taking place at a jeweler's office in of Rajnagar. When the entire security mechanism was anticipating the robbers to take the arrival route for escape, Dhruv was patrolling the basement. Dhruv's razor sharp thought processing helped him to apprehend the robbers without any fuss. This incident was covered extensively by the press and few shady characters began to take active interest in Dhruv! They analyzed that Dhruv was uncomfortable fighting against aliens. Rajnagar was witnessing crimes which made no sense. A sick and demented criminal is busy killing intellectuals and extracting their brain! One of the delegates to an international seminar, Miss Nataulia is concerned about her security and requests Dhruv to provide her security. Dhruv manages to save her from a robot which was sent to kill her. The situation is complicated with the appearance of the aliens who claim responsibility for the weird killings! Dhruv is baffled! Aliens are hell bent on extracting human brain! Scientists have declared that the robot which attacked Nataulia could be of an alien origin. Compounding his troubles, Shweta has been diagnosed of meningitis! Is it an alien race or a sick mind? Find out in a thrilling adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Shah Aur Maat(Check and Mate)

description: Chumba the man who could control magnetism with his will was a man who was haunted with a recurrent nightmare. In his dream he saw himself getting thrashed mercilessly from Dhruv. An incarnation of devil reaches out to Chumba and incites him to return to his evil ways. This devil promises Chumba his support and unimaginable powers in return of chumba's loyalty and devotion. The devil gives Chumba a device to stay in touch round the clock. In the outskirts of Rajnagar, Shyamli lived along with his grandfather who was a scholar in ancient Indian science and technology. Chumba sent one of his trusted lieutenants to extract a formulation from an ancient book. Sensing danger the scholar tore the page containing the formulation and asked Shyamli to take it to safety! Shyamli was able to locate Dhruv! The scholar tries to put up a fight against the assailant but lands up in coma instead! Despite their best attempts the assailant manages to transfer the crucial information to Chumba! The damage has been done! Chumba has got a rare formulation which threatens to cause wide scale destruction! The scholar is in coma where as Shyamli is inept to help Dhruv! Will the combination of devil and Chumba usher a reign of terror, now that they have the formulation! Read an adventure with magnetic features exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Aaya Chumba(Chumba is back)

description: Chumba was perceived dead in an explosion but it was a robot that met the dreadful end! Chumba was successful in escaping with Tarangi, his lieutenant who was under police custody! Chumba was extremely pleased with the smooth running of his plans as he had managed to neutralize his greatest enemy. He showed Tarangi the culmination of his hard work using the formulation! Chumba had managed to create universal solvent which could be contained only inside a strong magnetic field. Chumba now wished to usurp reign of neighboring country which had nuclear weapons! After annexing power of this nation he had prepared grand designs of his reign across the globe. To his horror, Chumba found that Dhruv had switched places with Tarangi and what he had witnessed in the police lock up was a farce! With the help of the devil Chumba is successful to trap Dhruv in a chamber with the universal solvent trickling into it! Chumba has set out on his conquest of this planet. Dhruv is inches away from a painful death. Will Dhruv rise up to the occasion and save the world from the evil reign of Chumba! Read an adventure which is an ode to bravery and determination, exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Chumba Samrat(Chumba king)

description: A recurrent nightmare haunts Natasha. In her dreams, Dhruv professes his love for Natasha but refuses to accept her as her life partner since she has chosen to become a terrorist and follow the foot steps of her father! Natasha is highly perturbed with these nightmares and appears to be totally shaken up! Unable to watch Natasha in trauma conspires to turn Dhruv into a criminal forcing him to surrender to the authorities! Once a criminal it would be easier to coerce Dhruv to join his gang. Dhruv falls into the trap and believes that he is a murderer! He surrenders and is put behind bars! But then a mysterious woman named Shala helps Dhruv to avoid further traps that wait for him! She helps him to escape from the lock up to prove his innocence and foil the treacherous plot masterminded by Grand Master Robo! Shala appears to be highly protective of Dhruv and takes grave risk to protect him from any danger! Shala incurs the wrath of Natasha for meddling in her affairs! Natasha is also feeling very Jealous of Shala who is displaying a strong emotion for Dhruv!! You won't believe it but its true! Our favorite super hero has been accused of committing a murder! Can his innocence be proved in the eyes of the law when Dhruv is adamant on admitting his guilt! The mystery unfolds exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Dhruv Hatyaara Hai(Dhruva is Murderer)

description: Shala's loyalty towards Dhruv and her exploits have earned the ire of Natasha! Natasha wants Shala to be captured alive and execute her. Robo appoints deputy commando I-1 to capture Shala alive. I-1 proposes to use Dhruv as bait to capture Shala! Though apprehensive about I-1's loyalty, Natasha gives her the clearance to go ahead with his planning! Dhruv is attacked by a monster and Shala is lured into the fight! I-1 succeeds in capturing Shala alive and presents her before Natasha! Not even in her wildest dreams could have Natasha imagined that Shweta had donned the mantle of Shala. She prevents her men from attacking Shweta and takes Shweta back to her house! Can all this be true or is there more than that meets the eye? Can she and Robo quell a rebellion which is very imminent? Is I-1 a man to be trusted or is he scheming a devious plan own! Grand Master Robo is at the mercy of I-1 who wishes to exterminate the father daughter duo along with Dhruv! Lot of questions remains unresolved if we are to believe that Shala is none other than Shweta! Robo, Dhruv, Natasha and Shweta have been trapped in a vicious conspiracy! Can they find a way out of their troubles? Solve this mysterious adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Shahenshah

description: The clock of evolution has been reversed. Mammoth, which was extinct for centuries, has been roaming on the streets of Rajnagar! His arrival has been augmented by snowfall in Rajnagar which was an unprecedented event in itself. Vanputra is attacked by goons who have a particular interest in the cylinders which Vanputra has been carrying along with him. Before things get out of control Dhruv joins the fight and manages to save Vanputra! On interrogation Dhruv finds out these goons were hired on contract to steal these cylinders. The mammoth and a snow robot attack a factory in Rajnagar which specialized in making coolants. Dhruv and Vanputra are joined by Dr. Varghese. Dr. Varghese tests the gasses contained in the cylinders and concludes that these gasses are very high grade refrigerants. A new breed of living being comes to Rajnagar in their quest for these refrigerants. They acknowledge themselves as Sheetans and begin to cause mayhem in the town. Now Dhruv and Vanputra are out to confront these creatures. Will they best the odds and win over these ice monsters. Who are these mysterious monsters? What is their motive behind stealing these refrigerants? Enjoy the chill in an exciting adventure with an unexpected twist in the story exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Sheetan(Satan)

description: Rajnagar was witnessing a bloody battle of supremacy between rival gangs. A meeting between two such gangs headed by Haroon and Shah respectively turned ugly. The crime lords ordered their henchmen to wipe off the rival gang. But Haroon and his team were superior and better prepared for the situation. They were able to crush the Shah gang along with its leader. Within no time Dhruv and a police helicopter reached the crime scene. Haroon did manage to give them the slip. Infuriated by the damage inflicted to an ancient temple a priest named Bhootbhooti decided to invoke death on these criminals! He begins a 3 day ritual to summon death in human form and rid this city of evil persons. Dr. Thaka a renowned psychologist rubbished the claims of the priest and claimed that such instances in the past can be often attributed to mass hysteria. Dhruv was in pursuit of death is it really an incarnation of death or is a sinister plan at work? Everything is pointing to wards the fact that an incarnation of death is cleansing the town of Rajnagar from evil people. Will Dhruv be forced to accept the fact before it's too late or will his haunch prove correct? Come face to face with death in this adventure available exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Dhruva Khatm

description: Dhruv has been asked to escort the police party transferring dangerous convicts, Zulu and Dr. Virus. The convicts rue the fact that Dhruv had spoiled their grand designs to rule the world. They were praying to find a way for their escape when luck favored them. Two space ships appeared on the horizon and after battling each other collided with the earth! Post explosion Dhruv had to face with a dreaded menace in the form of an alien who intended to destroy the planet! Dr. Virus is curious about this alien and wants to capture him to study its genetic composition. He wants to create a new monster using the alien gene. But the monster manages to possess the body of a police inspector who now transforms into a monster. Another alien joins in the fight and it seems the aliens are hell bent on killing each other! Dhruv has to stop the new entrant from killing the inspector who has morphed into a monster. The alien takes offense to Dhruv's view and begins to attach him instead. Dhruv shifts his entire focus on the new alien and allows Dr. Virus to kidnap the inspector and head for Zulu's secret hideout! Will Dr. Virus succeed in his evil designs to create new stains of monsters and unleash them on the planet? Dhruv is battling a host of aliens who have some amazing powers? Can he befriend the aliens to stop this evil spirit or will they continue to clash with each other? The mystery shall be revealed exclusively on Raj comics
name: Aant(The End)

description: At a neurological symposium for psychiatrists, Dr. Sodawala made a startling claim! He announced that he had developed a powerful machine named â€œNeuroguideâ€. The â€œNeuroguideâ€ could influence any human mind and make him act according to the directions of the man using it. It could also scan the human brain, detect anomalies and rectify them by making new connections between the neurons. Dr. Sodawala claimed that his invention will usher a revolution in psychiatry and shall go a long way in treating mentally sick patients. A bunch of criminals pretending to be lunatics stun the guard and head for the venue of the symposium. They also set free lunatics in the asylum to create mayhem and keep the guards busy. The leader of this gang attacks Dr. Sodawala and snatches the â€œNeuroguideâ€. Partho who was an assistant to Dr. Sodawala tries to resist but is unable to stop the gang. The Neuroguide is in wrong hands and Dhruv was worried. A lot of destruction can be caused if Neuroguide is used for an evil purpose. The plot gets exciting when an assassination attempt is made on the prime minister of India! Enjoy an adventure which will set your heart racing exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Doosra Dhruva

description: Scientists have succeeded in building a state of the art super computer which is equipped with enhanced artificial intelligence! The scientists have pinned great hopes on this computer to solve problems of the future. Black Cat is about to renounce her crime fighting ways! While she was dumping her dress at a garbage bin around midnight, she witnessed an abduction of an orphan beggar kid. Unable to restrain herself she began her pursuit of the abductors as Black Cat! She managed to rescue the kid temporarily but the abductors displayed super human strength to corner her! Dhruv joined the battle to tilt the scale in favor of Black Cat. After a prolonged battle Dhruv was able to knock off the assailants but to his utter surprise the kid vanished inside an alien ship. Both Dhruv and black cat were baffled by the motive behind abducting a beggar! Rajnagar is witnessing a new scare! An alien seems to digitize the buildings and other inanimate objects and making them disappear in thin air. Dhruv challenges the alien and engages him in a fight. Dhruv manages to outmaneuver the alien and with the help of friendly dolphins forcing the alien to retreat. Chaos is prevalent all around in Rajnagar with everything disappearing in thin air! The aliens have superior technology which cannot be matched by our science! Can the new super computer, using artificial intelligence find a solution to counter this threat? Get hooked to an exciting adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Digital

Contents
X-Men Vol. 1 #11
X-Men Vol. 1 #18
X-Men Vol. 1 #104
Vision And The Scarlet Witch Vol. 1 #4
name: The Triumph of Magneto!; If Iceman Should Fail--!; The Gentleman's Name is Magneto; Please Allow Me To Introduce Myself...!

description: Want to know what it takes to break into Marvel Comics like these guys? Then look no further than this two-part book which is a must-have for anyone wanting to be a Comic Book Breakout Star! After traveling the globe and meeting scores of talented illustrators, intrepid writer, editor and talent manager C.B. Cebulski is giving twelve rising star artists the opportunity to do their breakout work at Marvel Comics! But not only will BREAKING INTO COMICS THE MARVEL WAY showcase the work of these up-and-comers, C.B. will also provide an insider's commentary on how these artists got their work seen and what it was that landed them the gig. And with step-by-step submission information and a sample Marvel Comics script, these books are MUST HAVES for anyone interested in doing their breakout work and breaking into the comics industry!
name: Fantastic Four: Signals; Hammer And Sinew; Green Dreams; Butterfly Blade; Oh, The Places You'll Go!; Dead Man Talking

volume.name: Breaking Into Comics The Marvel Way!

description: Gus's baby sister Tilly is a nuisance. She destroys Gus's room, she steals his cookies, and basically makes his life a mess! But is Tilly a mutant? Gus sure thinks so, and he's called the mutant experts in to find out for sure! Will the X-Men discover the truth about Tilly ... or will Gus be too annoying for them to even care?
name: The Marvelous Adventures of Gus Beezer with the X-Men

volume.name: The Marvelous Adventures of Gus Beezer with the X-Men

description: AN ALL-NEW SERIES OF PAINTED ONE-SHOTS FROM MARVEL, RECAPTURING THE EARLIEST DAYS OF OUR GREATEST HEROES! The first of a series of quintessential, stand-alone, done-in-one stories by Paul Jenkins and Paolo Rivera, MYTHOS: X-MEN takes readers back to the formative days of Xavier's School for Gifted Youngsters, and recounts the first encounter between the nescient, teen-aged X-Men with their ultimate nemesis, Magneto! Filled with new detail and nuance, the MYTHOS books are also the perfect starter set for those readers new to the Marvel cast of characters, or to those who known them only from movies and television cartoons!
name: Mythos: X-Men

first_appearance_locations.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

location_credits.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

description:
Not an actual comic book.  Consists of posters. 
 
(From back cover) Children of the atom, students of Charles Xavier, warriors for a dream-they are the X-Men- Feared and hated by a world they have sworn to protect.
 
In these classic poster-sized shots witness the power of the strangest super-team of all, through their many incarnations.
name: Hot Shots: X-Men

description: A political opponent of mayor Shantidas approaches a shady character named Master Blaster to eliminate the mayor! Master blaster sends his hit man, a mutant named 'Grenade' to assassinate the mayor! As fate would have it Dhruv manages to reach the mayor just in time to save him from the lethal attack. The identity of the mastermind remains a mystery as the assassin is in coma. The children of mayor Shantaram who happened to accompany Dhruv pledge revenge against the man responsible for this attack. They find a clue in the form a letter in the litter of their dad's study! The boys follow the trail which leads them to a desolate farm house by the very man who had placed the contract to kill Shantaram! Dr. Musa places the assassin under his super vision as he was also conducting a research on explosive elements in the human mutants! Master Blaster has acquired designs of atom bomb and a small quantity of uranium! Master Blaster decides to test the atomic device at the same farm house which the kids wanted to investigate! Dhruv is totally unaware of the presence of the kids in the farmhouse? Can he nab Master Blaster and save the kids at the same time? Dhruv is facing a tricky situation! These mutants can explode at will and are unable to arrest the chain of events. Will Dhruv and Dr. Musa find a way out to help the mutants as well as get rid of master blaster? Find out in an explosive adventure exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Master Blaster

description: In the year 2279 senior Inspector Mitta is an ardent fan super commando Dhruv and pays lavish rewards to anyone who manages to obtain comics describing the adventures of the super hero! His friend's professor Prasa considers him a fool for doing so! Prasa has high esteem for technological inventions and considers technology superior to human brain! He devises a plot to test Dhruv! Dhruv is busy foiling a hostage crisis at Rajnagar prison. He is amazed to find a gorilla and an expert in mountaineering holding the jailor of the prison as hostage. They were seeking the release of their partners and the weapon which were captured in an encounter! Dhruv manages to trap the gorilla but was caught unawares by the extraordinary powers displayed by its trainer! During the battle that follows the mysterious assailant lands up in coma and the gorilla manages to escape! Dhruv is in for more surprise when he finds out that the confiscated weapons and ammunition were actually stolen from an army depot. Dhruv decides to go under cover as a major of the Indian Army. Grand Master Robo has been coaxed to give up his retirement by the mysterious King Kong! Can Dhruv and Natasha thwart Grand Master Robo and King Kong in their plans? Dhruv has acquired amazing super powers! What is the secret of these powers? Read an adventurous tale of fantasy exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Robot

description: Dhruv has been teleported to 2296 while an advanced Robot with artificial intelligence has replaced him in the year 2003. He has been summoned by professor Prasa to rein the mayhem during that age. The super computer which controlled the entire e-transactions of that age has been rendered non functional. The heavy duty silicon graphics processor of this computer has been stolen! People are unable to acquire goods and hence resorted to robbery and arson to fulfill their needs! Professor Prasa challenges Dhruv to retrieve the processor and usher peace and tranquility into their society! Dhruv is ready to under take this mission to save humanity. He has inspector Mitta to assist him in the case. Meanwhile in 2003 King Kong has abducted the robot of Dhruv. The robot enquires King Kong about the motive behind these smuggling operations. Taking the robot to be hapless, King Kong divulged his grand designs of eliminating the entire human race. But it seems that the robot has few aces up his sleeves. In 2006 Dhruv is in unfamiliar territory and has to face opponents who are quite advanced technologically! Can Dhruv outwit his superior opponents and retrieve the processor in time? Can the Robot over power King Kong and act as an apt replacement of Dhruv? The tale unfolds exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Super Commando Dhruva

description: Psychologist is a brilliant but devious character who rules the drug mafia in Rajnagar! He is a sadist who likes to research drugs using his patients as guinea pigs. His terror ensures that his henchman will embrace death rather than to divulge any details about his operation or his whereabouts! During his sessions Psychologist tries to unearth phobias of his patients and uses it to coax his patients into committing crimes! Dhruv encounters one such man but is grievously injured in the battle. Some unknown toxins have weakened his mind and doctors have recommended him to abstain from any form of combat for a week else he may face a nervous breakdown! Dr. Sulemani is a renowned psychiatrist himself and is an old adversary of Psychologist! Dhruv is taking the aid of Dr Sulemani to combat the menace of Psychologist. Parab an ardent fan of Dhruv and skilled in martial art had rescued Dhruv from his assailants. Now Psychologist is using Parab as the bait to trap Dhruv! Unaware of psychologist's plans both Parab and Dhruv head towards an unseen disaster! Parab has drowned in a river and is reported missing while Dhruv is in coma! Will psychologist spread his tentacles across Rajnagar or will an angel arise to curb the menace of Psychologist? Ravish this engrossing mystery exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Super Hero

description: Psychologist a dangerous criminal has succeeded in his evil designs! The biggest threat to his operations has been eliminated! Dhruv is in coma and is in no condition to protect the residents of Rajnagar from the sinister plans of Psychologist. But Psychologist was grossly mistaken if he thought he would win hands down. Shweta teams up with a new Super Hero and are spoiling the well laid plans of Psychologist. Who is the new savior of the town? He goes by the name of Farishta but his identity is a well guarded secret! Shweta sees on uncanny similarity between Dhruv and Farishta. But Dr. Sulemani vouches for the fact that Dhruv is yet to come out of his coma! Farishta is well aware of Dr. Sulemani's competency in the field of antidotes and hence seeks his help! Dr. Sulemani gives him an antidote for a wide range of neuron toxins used by psychologist! Farishta and Chandika team up to fight the cronies of psychologist and manage to find clue about Psychologist's next move! The antidote comes in handy when Farishta is attacked by the neurotoxins and renders the toxins useless! Black Cat joins the battle to save Rajnagar from this terror. Finally the mystery of Farishta is about to be revealed to one and all! But will the trio of Chandika, Black Cat and Farishta stop Psychologist before it's too late? Read the thrilling grand finale exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Farishta

description: Dhruv is disguised as a truck driver and goes undercover in a pharmacy factory which is suspected of manufacturing spurious drugs! Dhruv aims to unmask the true owner of the company before the factory is raided by officials, but is unable to avoid detection. The security guards identify him as an intruder and open fire at him. He manages to escape an attempt on his life but is knocked unconscious for few moments. But the rouges could not finish their job as they were stopped in their tracks by a shower of arrows! A self styled outlaw named Robin Hood attacks them with intent to rob them! He planned to distribute the loot among the needy! Robin Hood manages to rob them but now faces Dhruv who doesn't share his ideals. Dhruv is against this option as the poor would look for an easy way out and not make a conscious effort to earn their living. Dhruv stops him from getting away with the loot money. Robin Hood is furious with Dhruv for meddling in his affairs. He decides to teach Dhruv a lesson! The criminals masterminding the illegal business of spurious wish to widen the gulf between Dhruv and Robin Hood to butter their own cause! They lay a trap for both of them! Will they succeed in their attempt? Dhruv, Robin Hood and the criminals clash in a three sided battle to champion their cause. Who shall emerge victorious in this contest? Can Dhruv bring the outlaw back to the main stream? Will the mastermind behind these entire operations be unmasked? Seek your answers in this enthralling adventure exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Robin Hood
